{"tid":1513263,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒燶車位了】嘉湖車位113.8萬沽 業主持貨4個月蝕14%","createTime":"2019-08-28T09:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:28:36.000Z","uid":66271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d934f4c8e5ed96b007a4e30149f99b9963a148f","tid":1513263,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190828/s00011/61fde3d30105b60eecaed95c5ef0b1a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190828%2Fs00011%2F61fde3d30105b60eecaed95c5ef0b1a3.jpg&h=dbb8777d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會局勢持續動盪，個別車位業主寧蝕讓提早離場。中原分行經理曾芷妍表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊翠湖居一個單號車位，業主早前叫價125萬元放售，新近減價11.2萬元或9%後，以113.8萬元沽出。<br />\n<br />\n曾指出，原業主見本港局勢不穩，有意重組投資組合而提早放售車位，而上述車位於今年4月以133萬元購入，現帳面蝕逾19萬元或14%。<br />\n<br />\n以車位現市值月租2500至2700元計，新業主料可享約2.7厘租金回報率。"},{"pid":"20fda0530d2cfd439d95899ab3464c89f5b39eb0","tid":1513263,"uid":33125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:03:45.000Z","msg":"叫價-10% 炒燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ce4fd5796b0ab55b6b9bc3244d452f53a45530","tid":1513263,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9c0e9dfd2904165171a7a67c113489b57061a6","tid":1513263,"uid":39182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20fda0530d2cfd439d95899ab3464c89f5b39eb0","tid":1513263,"uid":33125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:03:45.000Z","msg":"叫價-10% 炒燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\